## Download Resilience

### Partial Download Recovery

- [ ] Download uses chunked transfer with per-chunk CRC
- [ ] Download progress is persisted (can resume after power loss)
- [ ] Flash is written sequentially (no random writes during download)
- [ ] Incomplete download does not corrupt inactive slot metadata
- [ ] Timeout on download: if no progress for 5 minutes, abort and retry

### Bandwidth and Storage

| Constraint | Approach |
|-----------|----------|
| Slow connection (< 10 kbps) | Delta updates (binary diff) |
| Limited flash | Streaming decompression (zlib with fixed window) |
| Unreliable link | Chunked download with resume |
| Metered connection | Compressed images, schedule for off-peak |

